# scaffolding_example (Data Source)

Example data source

## Example Usage

```terraform
data "intelcloud_machine_images" "images" {
  most_recent = true
  filters = [
    {
      name   = "name"
      values = ["ubuntu-2204-jammy"]
    }
  ]
}
```

## Schema

### Optional

- `most_recent` (Boolean) Return order by most recent 

### Read-Only

- `id` (String) machine identifier
